Colombian Navy Searching for 15 Kidnapped Off Pacific Coast

-- B y   R a n d a l l   W o o d s
-- 
2011-09-10T15:33:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-10/colombian-navy-searching-for-15-kidnapped-off-pacific-coast.html
Colombia ’s Navy is searching for 15
boat passengers who were kidnapped along the Pacific coast, the
Navy said in a  statement  posted on its  website  yesterday.  The coast guard has recovered the boat and is questioning
two members of its crew who were left behind yesterday after the
kidnapping, the Navy said. The statement didn’t provide
additional details on the kidnapping.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Woods in Santiago at 
 rwoods13@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Joshua Goodman  at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net . 